name: Dubitando Ad Veritatem Pervenimus
description: Ad Hoc Orquestra is a project based on collective improvisation, creating music in real time and promoting the encounter between multiple artists. Dubitando Ad Veritatem Pervenimus was created and recorded live in 2018 by Bernardo Bauer; Daniel Tamietti; Matheus Felix; P.C. Guimarães; Yuri Vellasco; Vinícius Mendes; Conducted by Guilherme Peluci. Recorded live at Bioma and released in November 12, 2018.
